{"tid":702986,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"nowTV 即日停播英超頻道! 2018-2019 英超播放安排未定","createTime":"2018-06-15T11:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T19:56:57.000Z","uid":4741,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c39f37e2f1895b88aeec6984279b0753756cc855","tid":702986,"uid":4741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1142/25819/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1142%2F25819%2F1%2F&d=YnwWlSBWHhr3D8QJ6eb0lJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=d5951691\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1142/25819/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157cff1ffa8e7915cfa51bd1c7df2cd133b4f35d","tid":702986,"uid":4741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"copy from facebook<br />\n<br />\n各位同事:<br />\n<br />\n由於樂視體育(LeSports HK)清盤， ch.620 and ch.621兩條頻道會暫停直到另行通知，<br />\n<br />\n1.\t今天下午2點左右，英超聯賽的所有頻道（ch.620-629 / ch.610）會變藍灰畫面 (channel slate)<br />\n2.    英超視頻點播庫(VOD) 將於今天中午左右移除<br />\n3.    所有於數碼平台（電視，APP，網絡）上的英超頻道logo和頻道名稱將從今天下午四點開始更改為以下logo<br />\n<br />\n4.    所有sales script應該省略提及英超聯賽，所有印刷品有提及英超聯賽應暫停使用<br />\n<br />\nChannel Slate &amp; EPG Message: <br />\n<br />\n2017/2018英超季度已完結，暫時並沒有賽事直播，多謝收看。<br />\nThe 2017/2018 Premier League season has ended and there are no live matches at the moment.  <br />\n<br />\nUpdated有關英超播影問題FAQ:<br />\n<br />\n Q: 點解ch.620 / ch.621/ 英超VOD無嘢睇，你哋係下季有無英超播?<br />\nA: 我們與英超合作多年，現已積極與他們商討接手播放權，遲些會公布確實的2018/2019季度英超直播的安排。現時請繼續於其他體育頻道收看各大體壇盛事。<br />\n<br />\nQ: Why there is no program on ch.620 / ch.621 / Premier League VOD, will Now TV still broadcast Premier League for next season?<br />\nA: We have worked with Premier League for many years, we are actively pursuing the takeover of Premier League broadcasting right, and we will soon announce the confirmed broadcasting arrangement for season 2018/2019.  You may tune-in to watch more live events on other sports channels for now.<br />\n<br />\nKIS:<br />\n有關英超播放協議已在商討中，2018/2019 英超播放安排將稍後公布。<br />\nThe broadcasting of Premier League is in deliberation, arrangement on the season 2018/2019 Premier League broadcasting will be announced in due course."},{"pid":"5310e626d4e008d5c0c01deeea31d33b4aa0bbd4","tid":702986,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"Cctvb go"},{"pid":"07393130264fd37df68f43ae5728f52f03fef4db","tid":702986,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"in now we 7s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9039879ef62313479e37cdf99d45bbafe86c7c1d","tid":702986,"uid":90321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"唔洗急等傾好份新約就上番架，唔係now唔通cctvb會買到黎播咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5441ae6926fdf028463d1fa35a02c18257d9e5a3","tid":702986,"uid":34468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"新標未定，舊標完咗，停咗先好正路啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d38f0148cd4b113a3f690729a22aa5e2068bef","tid":702986,"uid":27485,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"下 隻sales 話下年都係佢地我先續"},{"pid":"ae3cf6659fb6ca788fd0ee7fd5fdb3630cd35a1c","tid":702986,"uid":4462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱問仲話有1819我先續喎"},{"pid":"548ae1e4ac46f1020163b4466cd318edd79b706e","tid":702986,"uid":4741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5441ae6926fdf028463d1fa35a02c18257d9e5a3","tid":702986,"uid":34468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"201